title: Talent Management System
description: This system was developed during my internship at Africom Company. It is a job portal that acts as a bridge between job seekers and companies, facilitating the recruitment process by connecting talent with potential employers.

title: Human Resource Management System
description: This project was developed for Akufada Microfinance as part of a volunteer initiative. It is a Human Resource Management System designed to automate key HR tasks for the company.

title: Personal Portfolio
description: This project was created to showcase my skills and experience in a clear and simplified way. It reflects my ability to design and develop functional systems while maintaining a focus on user experience and performance.

title: Fruit and Vegetables Recognition System using CNN
description: This project utilizes Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) for the identification of fruits and vegetables from images. It demonstrates my ability to implement machine learning algorithms and computer vision techniques to solve real-world classification problems.

title: Fruit and Vegetables Recognition System using Random Forest
description: This project applies the Random Forest algorithm for the classification of fruits and vegetables based on image features. It highlights my skills in machine learning model training and feature engineering for improved accuracy in image classification tasks.
